## Slide 9: Why This Works
**Mathematical vs AI Approaches**

| Aspect | Our Approach | Pure AI/ML |
|--------|--------------|------------|
| **Explainable** | ‚úÖ Full traceability | ‚ùå Black box |
| **Data Needs** | ‚úÖ Small datasets | ‚ùå Massive data |
| **Reliability** | ‚úÖ Guaranteed constraints | ‚ùå Probabilistic |
| **Maintenance** | ‚úÖ Easy rule updates | ‚ùå Requires retraining |
| **Engineering Trust** | ‚úÖ Auditable logic | ‚ùå Statistical confidence |

